Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:29.37,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(100,300)\pos(785,245)}带着些许悲寂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:33.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(100,300)\pos(785,245)}再做一次努力尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:41.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(100,300)\pos(785,245)}这次要高到突破天际
